---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Economic Modelling | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="AI-assisted economic modelling built on Principal Economics' extensive modelling work, frameworks, and intellectual property."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Economic Modelling
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Economic models made easier to interrogate, explain, and use.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI builds on Principal Economics’ extensive modelling work and intellectual property to create AI-assisted systems for scenario analysis, appraisal, forecasting, and decision support.
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
      >
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The opportunity
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Economic models are powerful, but often difficult to access.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Economic models can support high-value decisions, but they are often complex, technical, and difficult for non-specialist users to interrogate.
          </p>

          <p>
            PrincipalAI adds an intelligence layer over economic models, helping users ask questions, explore scenarios, interpret results, and understand the implications of different assumptions.
          </p>

          <p>
            This capability builds directly on Principal Economics’ existing modelling frameworks, applied project experience, and proprietary intellectual property across economic appraisal, impact analysis, forecasting, and policy evaluation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          AI-assisted modelling for decisions where economic consequences matter.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Scenario analysis
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Test how outcomes change under alternative assumptions, shocks, policies, investments, and future pathways.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Model interpretation
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Help users understand model outputs, drivers, sensitivities, assumptions, and limitations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Appraisal support
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Support cost-benefit analysis, economic impact assessment, investment cases, and policy evaluation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Decision reporting
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Generate structured summaries that translate model results into clear advice and decision implications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Modelling foundations
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Built on Principal Economics’ modelling capability.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI draws on Principal Economics’ extensive modelling experience across transport, infrastructure, energy, climate, health, housing, regulation, and public policy.
          </p>

          <p>
            This includes applied frameworks for economic appraisal, cost-benefit analysis, spatial analysis, forecasting, scenario testing, impact assessment, and economy-wide modelling.
          </p>

          <p>
            Rather than exposing technical model architecture publicly, PrincipalAI turns these modelling assets into usable decision-support systems that help organisations explore options and understand economic consequences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          Example applications
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Economic intelligence for complex policy and investment questions.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Infrastructure and transport
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              Explore investment options, accessibility impacts, economic benefits, distributional effects, and network-related consequences.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Energy and climate
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              Assess market conditions, transition pathways, emissions impacts, adaptation options, and resilience investments.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Policy and regulation
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              Support regulatory analysis, economic impact assessment, policy evaluation, and evidence-based advice.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Health, housing, and communities
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              Understand vulnerability, access, wellbeing, service demand, equity, and place-based economic outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            The value is not the AI alone. It is the model intelligence behind it.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many AI tools can generate text about economics. PrincipalAI is designed to connect AI to economic models, datasets, assumptions, appraisal frameworks, and domain expertise.
          </p>

          <p>
            This allows users to move from general explanation to applied decision intelligence grounded in Principal Economics’ modelling capability and accumulated intellectual property.
          </p>

          <p>
            The result is a practical interface between sophisticated economic analysis and the real decisions organisations need to make.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Turn economic models into decision intelligence.
        </h2>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about AI-assisted economic modelling, scenario analysis, appraisal systems, and decision-support platforms.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
        >
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
